<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈把彼得抱进房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的脚在流血，他的脸很苍白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弗里斯医生用绷带绑好他的脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 鲍比小声问医生：“他不会跛脚吧？不会要一直用拐杖吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>医生告诉她不用担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来的一个星期，彼得休息，菲利斯在花园里玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而鲍比却在想念着爸爸：为什么他还没有回来？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈是不是有事没有告诉他们？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天鲍比的问题就得到了答案。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比去车站帮彼得拿杂志。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些是旧杂志，是留在火车上或者候车室里别人不要的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯说他们可以拿回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我用报纸和绳子帮你把杂志捆起来吧。”帕克斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从一堆报纸里拿了一张旧报纸，把杂志包了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回家的路上，鲍比在火车道口停下来等一列火车经过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比把杂志放在道口栏杆上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她低头看了看包着杂志的报纸，看到一个大标题……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一切就像是一个噩梦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比一口气跑回自己的房间，锁上门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比又拿出报纸。报纸头版写着：间谍被判刑五年！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“间谍”的名字就是她爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我知道了。”鲍比自言自语地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃晚餐时，鲍比想假装什么事都没发生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是她做不到，她的眼睛已经哭红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？”妈妈问她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140478</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没事。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃完晚餐，妈妈来到鲍比的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到底怎么了？”她想知道发生了什么事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比把报纸给妈妈看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比！”妈妈喊道，“你不会相信，对吧？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你不会相信爸爸是间谍，对吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不相信！”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他诚实善良，没有做错任何事。”妈妈说，“我们必须记住这一点。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到底发生了什么事？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还记得来找你爸爸的两位客人吗？”妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们说爸爸是间谍，把政府的机密卖给了其他国家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在你爸爸办公室的桌子里发现了一些信，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警察们看到那些信以后，就认定你爸爸是间谍了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是为什么那些信会在他的桌子里呢？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是有人故意放在那里的。”妈妈回答，“那个人才是真正的间谍。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不知道。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不能向警察解释说爸爸不是间谍吗？”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“试过了，但是他们不听。”妈妈伤心地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我各种方法都试过了，现在我们只能等待。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不要再说这件事了，也不要告诉彼得和菲利斯。鲍比，你要坚强点儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比想帮助爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，她给老先生写了一封信，希望他能再帮助他们一次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亲爱的朋友：请您看看这张报纸，这是关于我爸爸的事，但它不是真的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈说，是有人把信放进了爸爸的桌子里，但是没有人相信她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您又善良又聪明，您可以帮我们找到真正的间谍吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得和菲利斯还不知道爸爸在监狱。请您帮帮我！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您的朋友：鲍比</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比把报纸的第一页撕下来，和信一起放进信封。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她请站长第二天早上把信交给老先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，她只能等待。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老先生会再次帮助他们吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>